new-york-meet-me-bathroom-lizzy-goodman-interview-2117913"><em>口述</em>历史书。</a> <em>《约克城2001-2011》</em>在被<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/meet-me-in-the-bathroom-review-dissecting-new-yorks-early-noughties-rock-revolution-3411510">拍成同名纪录片</a>之前上映。</p><p> LCD Soundsystem 最近完成了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-trio-boro-new-york-city-residencies-buy-tickets-3507915">纽约市三个不同行政区为期 12 场的驻场演出</a>，他们在那里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lcd-soundsystem-perform-one-touch-for-the-first-time-ever-at-new-york-residency-3542725">首次现场表演了《This Is Happening》中的《One Touch》</a> ，并翻唱了 The Pogues 的《Fairy》向 Shane MacGowan 致敬纽约故事》。</p><p>他们最终将于 12 月 30 日和 31 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-new-years-san-francisco-shows-3534190">在旧金山举行两场演出</a>，然后在 2024 年举行一系列欧洲演出，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">8 月 23 日在伦敦 All Points East 举行的头条新闻</a>。请访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fall-points-east-tickets%2Fartist%2F5245909" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取门票和更多信息。</p><p>该乐队最后一次发行音乐是在 2022 年，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-release-their-first-song-in-five-years-new-body-rhumba-3320310">一首名为“New Body Rhumba”的歌曲</a>是为诺亚·鲍姆巴赫 (Noah Baumbach) 的《白噪音》 <em>(White Noise)</em>的配乐而写的。他们最后一次发行全长专辑是在 2017 年，其中有《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lcd-soundsystem-american-dream-review-2133039-2133039">美国梦</a>》， <em>NME</em>称这张唱片“保留了概括地点和时间的不可思议的力量。这是一次谨慎的回归，而不是一次胜利——这证明了 LCD 音响系统非常具有 2017 年风格。”</p><p>这篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-these-exclusive-shots-from-new-photo-book-on-early-years-of-dfa-records-3562323">《看看这些来自 DFA 唱片公司早年的新写真集的独家照片》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 The Libertines 翻唱 The Pogues 的《Fairy Tale Of New York》向 Shane MacGowan 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-cover-the-pogues-fairy-tale-of-new-york-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3562319?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=浪荡子翻唱纽约波格斯童话向肖恩·麦高恩致敬Anagricel DuranThu, 21 Dec 2023 15:24:26 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3562319 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪子乐队和肖恩·麦高恩。图片来源：Jim Dyson 和 Frans Schellekens，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “RIP Shane，这是给你的，伙计 x”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-cover-the-pogues-fairy-tale-of-new-york-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3562319">The Libertines 翻唱 The Pogues 的《Fairy Tale Of New York》向 Shane MacGowan 致敬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪子乐队和肖恩·麦高恩。图片来源：Jim Dyson 和 Frans Schellekens，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/The-Libertines-and-Shane-MacGowan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a>翻唱了<a href="/artists/the-pogues">The Pogues</a>的《Fairy Tale Of New York》，向该乐队已故主唱<a href="/artists/shane-macgowan">Shane MacGowan</a>致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/shane-macgowan-obituary-the-pogues-3551303">Shane MacGowan，1957-2023：一位不妥协、混乱的人</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队由<a href="/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂 (Pete Doherty)</a> 、<a href="/artists/carl-barat">卡尔·巴拉特 (Carl Barât</a> )、约翰·哈索尔 (John Hassall) 和加里·鲍威尔 (Gary Powell) 组成，在他们的 Instagram 官方页面上分享了一段视频，视频中巴拉特在钢琴上演奏了著名的圣诞曲子，他和多尔蒂也跟着一起唱歌。视频的标题是：“RIP Shane，这个是给你的，matey x”。</p><p>两天后，他们发布了另一段整个乐队在一场亲密演出中在舞台上表演《纽约童话》的视频。”另一张献给 Shane x，”标题写道。</p><p>麦高恩于 11 月 30 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-line-the-streets-of-dublin-for-shane-macgowan-funeral-3556189">因肺炎在医院去世</a>，享年 65 岁，并于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bono-johnny-depp-nick-cave-lead-tributes-to-shane-macgowan-at-funeral-3556257">12 月 8 日下葬。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-line-the-streets-of-dublin-for-shane-macgowan-funeral-3556189">他的葬礼在爱尔兰蒂珀雷里郡尼纳举行，葬礼前粉丝们聚集在都柏林街道两旁</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/johnny-depp-salutes-maestro-shane-macgowan-during-funeral-reading-3556302">约翰尼也出席了葬礼。德普</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glen-hansard-and-lisa-oneill-perform-fairytale-of-new-york-at-shane-macgowans-funeral-3556366">格伦·汉萨德</a>和爱尔兰总统迈克尔·D·希金斯。 </p><blockquote 